---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Img from "../assets/img_1.webp";
---

<div
  class="m-1 p-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#161d1d] text-[#cdd0d4] rounded-lg flex flex-col justify-center items-center"
>
  <div class="m-1 p-1 flex flex-row justify-center items-center">
    <h3 id="section_project" class="m-1 p-1 text-2xl font-semibold text-[#8ccfc4]">📡 Proyecto 1</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="m-1 p-1 flex flex-col justify-center align-center">
    <ul class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
      <div
        class="m-1 p-1 mb-0 border-[#314949] border-[1px] flex flex-row justify-center items-center rounded-lg"
      >
        <strong class="ml-2 pl-2 text-[#78c08e] font-semibold border-[#314949]">
          Gallery-Jct - Galería de Imágenes
        </strong>
        <li
          class="m-0 p-0 text-[#77a3b8] font-bold border-[1px] border-[#314949] border-x-0 border-y-0 border-b-0 border-t-0"
        >
          <span class="text-[#168649]">┃</span>2024
        </li>
      </div>
      <p
        class="m-1 p-1 rounded-lg flex flex-row justify-center items-center text-center"
      >
        Galería de fotos interactiva desarrollada desde cero <br /> con JavaScript
        vanilla, Node.js y Vite, presentando <br /> una colección de imágenes con
        navegación fluida.
      </p>
      <p
        class="m-2 p-2 border-[1px] border-[#314949] rounded-lg flex flex-row justify-center items-center"
      >
        <Image src={Img} alt="Img" width={370} title="Jssbsbbsbs" />
      </p>
      <div
        id="div-icons"
        class="m-1 p-1 rounded-lg flex flex-row justify-center items-center"
      >
        🌐 <b>HTML</b>
        <span class="m-1 p-1 text-[#524d4d]">|</span>
        🎨 <b>CSS</b>
        <span class="m-1 p-1 text-[#524d4d]">|</span>
        ⚡ <b>JavaScript</b>
        <span class="m-1 p-1 text-[#524d4d]">|</span>
        🚀 <b>Vite.js</b>
      </div>
      <center
        class="m-1 p-1 rounded-lg flex flex-row justify-center items-center"
      >
        <button
          class="m-[2.5px] p-[2.5px] text-[#cdd0d4] flex flex-row justify-center items-center border-[1px] border-[#314949] hover:text-[#8ccfc4] rounded-lg"
        >
          🖥️
          <strong
            class="mr-[2.5px] p-[3px] cursor-pointer hover:text-[#36e685]"
          >
            <a
              href="https://github.com/jeanctech/gallery-jct"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">Ver Codigo Fuente</a
            >
          </strong>
        </button>
        <p class="m-0.5"></p>
        <button
          class="m-[2.5px] p-[2.5px] text-[#cdd0d4] flex flex-row justify-center items-center border-[1px] border-[#314949] hover:text-[#8ccfc4]
        rounded-lg"
        >
          🌐
          <strong
            class="mr-[2.5px] p-[3px] cursor-pointer hover:text-[#36e685]"
          >
            <a
              href="https://gallery-jct.netlify.app/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">Ir al Sitio Web</a
            >
          </strong>
        </button>
      </center>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

